## Supported Languages

HighlightedCodeBlock supports all languages that Shiki supports, including:

| Language | Code |
|----------|------|
| JavaScript | `javascript` / `js` |
| TypeScript | `typescript` / `ts` |
| Svelte | `svelte` |
| Rust | `rust` |
| Python | `python` / `py` |
| Go | `go` |
| HTML | `html` |
| CSS | `css` |
| JSON | `json` |
| Bash | `bash` / `sh` |
| SQL | `sql` |
| Markdown | `markdown` / `md` |

See the [Shiki documentation](https://shiki.style/languages) for the full list.

